text: Jake Bensted (born 4 March 1994) is an Australian judoka. He won a bronze medal at the 2014 Commonwealth Games and competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics, where he was eliminated in the second bout. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Australia Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in judo Category:Commonwealth Games bronze medallists for Australia Category:Judoka at the 2014 Commonwealth Games
